msgstr "该值以透视正确的方式插值。这是默认值。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:548
msgid "Uniforms"
msgstr "统一值（Uniforms）"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:550
msgid ""
"Passing values to shaders is possible. These are global to the whole shader "
"and are called *uniforms*. When a shader is later assigned to a material, "
"the uniforms will appear as editable parameters in it. Uniforms can't be "
"written from within the shader."
msgstr ""
"可以将值传递给着色器。这些对于整个着色器是全局的，称为 *统一值（uniforms）*。"
"稍后将着色器分配给材质时，*统一值（uniforms）* 将在其中显示为可编辑参数。不能"
"从着色器内部编写 *统一值（uniforms）*。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:560
msgid ""
"You can set uniforms in the editor in the material. Or you can set them "
"through GDScript:"
msgstr ""
"您可以在材质的编辑器中设置 ``uniform``。或者您可以通过GDScript设置它们："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:566
msgid ""
"The first argument to ``set_shader_param`` is the name of the uniform in the "
"shader. It must match *exactly* to the name of the uniform in the shader or "
"else it will not be recognized."
msgstr ""
"``set_shader_param`` t的第一个参数是着色器中统一值的名称。它必须 *完全* 与着"
"色器中统一值的名称匹配，否则将无法被识别。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:569
msgid ""
"Any GLSL type except for *void* can be a uniform. Additionally, Godot "
"provides optional shader hints to make the compiler understand for what the "
"uniform is used."
msgstr ""
"除 *void* 外的任何GLSL类型都可以是一个统一值。此外，Godot提供了可选的着色器提"
"示，以使编译器了解使用的是什么统一值。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/shading_language.rst:580
msgid ""
"It's important to understand that textures that are supplied as color "
"require hints for proper sRGB->linear conversion (i.e. ``hint_albedo``), as "
"Godot’s 3D engine renders in linear color space."
msgstr ""
"请务必理解，作为颜色提供的纹理需要提示以正确进行sRGB->线性转换（即 "
"``hint_albedo``），因为Godot的3D引擎在线性颜色空间中进行渲染。"

